vernac_cmds: Hypothesis Aeq_dec : forall x y : A, {x = y} + {x <> y}.
Fixpoint set_add (a : A) (x : set) {struct x} : set := match x with | nil => a :: nil | a1 :: x1 => match Aeq_dec a a1 with | left _ => a1 :: x1 | right _ => a1 :: set_add a x1 end end.
Fixpoint set_mem (a : A) (x : set) {struct x} : bool := match x with | nil => false | a1 :: x1 => match Aeq_dec a a1 with | left _ => true | right _ => set_mem a x1 end end.
Fixpoint set_remove (a : A) (x : set) {struct x} : set := match x with | nil => empty_set | a1 :: x1 => match Aeq_dec a a1 with | left _ => set_remove a x1 | right _ => a1 :: set_remove a x1 end end.
Fixpoint set_inter (x : set) : set -> set := match x with | nil => fun y => nil (A:=A) | a1 :: x1 => fun y => if set_mem a1 y then a1 :: set_inter x1 y else set_inter x1 y end.
Fixpoint set_union (x y : set) {struct y} : set := match y with | nil => x | a1 :: y1 => set_add a1 (set_union x y1) end.
Fixpoint set_diff (x : set) : set -> set := fun y => match x with | nil => nil (A:=A) | a1 :: x1 => if set_mem a1 y then set_diff x1 y else set_add a1 (set_diff x1 y) end.
Definition set_In : A -> set -> Prop := In (A:=A).
Lemma Set_remove1 : forall (B : set) (x : A), ~ set_In x (set_remove x B).
induction B as [| a B HrecB].
Lemma set_In_dec : forall (a : A) (x : set), {set_In a x} + {~ set_In a x}.
intro Eq; rewrite Eq; left; auto with datatypes.
unfold not in |- *; intros; right; intro.
Lemma set_mem_ind : forall (B : Set) (P : B -> Prop) (y z : B) (a : A) (x : set), (set_In a x -> P y) -> P z -> P (if set_mem a x then y else z).
simple induction x; simpl in |- *; intros.
elim (Aeq_dec a a0); auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_mem_correct1 : forall (a : A) (x : set), set_mem a x = true -> set_In a x.
intros a0 l; elim (Aeq_dec a a0); auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_mem_correct2 : forall (a : A) (x : set), set_In a x -> set_mem a x = true.
intros a0 l; elim (Aeq_dec a a0); auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_mem_complete1 : forall (a : A) (x : set), set_mem a x = false -> ~ set_In a x.
intros a0 l; elim (Aeq_dec a a0).
unfold not in |- *; intros; elim H1; auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_mem_complete2 : forall (a : A) (x : set), ~ set_In a x -> set_mem a x = false.
intros a0 l; elim (Aeq_dec a a0).
intros; elim H0; auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_add_intro1 : forall (a b : A) (x : set), set_In a x -> set_In a (set_add b x).
unfold set_In in |- *; simple induction x; simpl in |- *.
elim (Aeq_dec b a0); right; [ assumption | auto with datatypes ].
Lemma set_add_intro2 : forall (a b : A) (x : set), a = b -> set_In a (set_add b x).
unfold set_In in |- *; simple induction x; simpl in |- *.
elim (Aeq_dec b a0); [ rewrite Hab; intro Hba0; rewrite Hba0; simpl in |- *; auto with datatypes | auto with datatypes ].
Lemma set_add_intro : forall (a b : A) (x : set), a = b \/ set_In a x -> set_In a (set_add b x).
intros a b x [H1| H2]; auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_add_elim : forall (a b : A) (x : set), set_In a (set_add b x) -> a = b \/ set_In a x.
simpl in |- *; intros [H1| H2]; auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_add_not_empty : forall (a : A) (x : set), set_add a x <> empty_set.
intros; elim (Aeq_dec a a0); intros; discriminate.
Lemma set_union_intro1 : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a x -> set_In a (set_union x y).
simple induction y; simpl in |- *; auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_union_intro2 : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a y -> set_In a (set_union x y).
intros; elim H0; auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_union_intro : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a x \/ set_In a y -> set_In a (set_union x y).
intros; elim H; auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_union_elim : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a (set_union x y) -> set_In a x \/ set_In a y.
Lemma set_inter_intro : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a x -> set_In a y -> set_In a (set_inter x y).
simpl in |- *; intros a0 l Hrec y [Ha0a| Hal] Hy.
elim (set_mem a y); simpl in |- *; intros.
absurd (set_In a y); auto with datatypes.
elim (set_mem a0 y); [ right; auto with datatypes | auto with datatypes ].
Lemma set_inter_elim1 : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a (set_inter x y) -> set_In a x.
simpl in |- *; intros a0 l Hrec y.
elim (set_mem a0 y); simpl in |- *; intros.
Lemma set_inter_elim2 : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a (set_inter x y) -> set_In a y.
unfold set_In, set_inter in |- *; unfold In in |- *; tauto.
simpl in |- *; intros a0 l Hrec y.
elim (set_mem a0 y); simpl in |- *; intros.
elim H0; [ intro Hr; rewrite <- Hr; eauto with datatypes | eauto with datatypes ].
Lemma set_inter_elim : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a (set_inter x y) -> set_In a x /\ set_In a y.
Lemma set_diff_intro : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a x -> ~ set_In a y -> set_In a (set_diff x y).
simpl in |- *; intros a0 l Hrec y [Ha0a| Hal] Hay.
elim (set_mem a y); [ intro Habs; discriminate Habs | auto with datatypes ].
elim (set_mem a0 y); auto with datatypes.
Lemma set_diff_elim1 : forall (a : A) (x y : set), set_In a (set_diff x y) -> set_In a x.
simpl in |- *; intros a0 l Hrec y; elim (set_mem a0 y).
Definition set_prod : set A -> set B -> set (A * B) := list_prod (A:=A) (B:=B).
Definition set_power : set A -> set B -> set (set (A * B)) := list_power (A:=A) (B:=B).
Definition set_map : (A -> B) -> set A -> set B := map (A:=A) (B:=B).
Definition set_fold_left : (B -> A -> B) -> set A -> B -> B := fold_left (A:=B) (B:=A).
Definition set_fold_right (f : A -> B -> B) (x : set A) (b : B) : B := fold_right f b x.
